column5: Beautiful home, perfect for A&M Aggies games, College Station, Texas. Sleeps 7 in beds, 2 on couches. Just 10 minutes drive to Kyle field. Quiet, safe neighborhood. Gorgeous kitchen. Gorgeous outdoor living with heated spa and pool. Perfect getaway for families and some friends. No large parties or events, please.
column8: Beautiful Aggieland home, sleeps 7+, pool & spa!
